avon products avp sees higher earnings avon products inc the diversifed conglomerate that had a strong turn around in said it expects sales and earnings to climb higher this year in its annual report the company also said it expects to maintain its current annual two dlr dividend on the basis of continued upward earnings in avon s operational earnings rose pct to mln dlrs from mln dlrs a year earlier and sales rose pct to billion dlrs it said the dlrs a share earned last year was the highest in five years but still well below the company s all time high of dlrs a share in reuter 